  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileParser
    A file parser that will take in a file of raw comma separated values (csv) and create a map that maps their value to their index location.
    QAnimationTabbedPane
    An tabbed animation area used to display the probability histogram of the simulators states and the vector rotation of Grover's Algorithm.
    QuantumGuiFrame
    The starting point for the entire program that contains the main function.
    QuantumGuiPanel
    The main panel placed into the frame on launching the program.
    QuantumMenuBar
    The class the handles all of the menu bar operations for the program which includes opening a file for test data and opening the help screen to explain program usage.
    QViewModel
    A class that interfaces between model code and the GUI.
